ate-600\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav></header><main><div class=\"w-full bg-white overflow-hidden\"><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-14 md:py-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><span class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs uppercase tracking-wider inline-flex\">Support Center</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-6 leading-tight text-slate-900\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">We&#x27;re Here to <br/><span class=\"text-blue-600\">Help.</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-slate-500 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">Whether you&#x27;re looking for technical support, billing inquiries, or just want to say hi, our community-focused team is ready to assist.</p></div><div class=\"relative flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[320px] sm:max-w-[420px] lg:max-w-[520px] aspect-4/3\"><div class=\"absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-blue-100 blur-2xl opacity-70\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-[24px] sm:rounded-[32px] md:rounded-[40px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl z-10\"><img alt=\"Support team working\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fteams%2Fcontact-team.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fteams%2Fcontact-team.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fteams%2Fcontact-t